Copy of Home | Chez L'Amour top of page About Menu Events Contact More Use tab to navigate through the menu items. a place to fall in love SERVICES Turn your dream into a reality DISCOVER Services Villa Magnolia is St. Augustine’s leading destination for romance, entertainment, and sweet endings. Home to Magnolia Music Hall, where superstars grace the stage, and Magnolia Dessert Bistro, where the spotlight is on artisanal treats, Villa Magnolia is located in the heart of the downtown historic district. The majestic colonial revival architecture, beautifully landscaped gardens, and luxurious mid-century modern interiors make Villa Magnolia perfect for any private occasion. Join us for live jazz and a glass of wine paired with one of our exclusive desserts crafted by the award-winning patissier of Creme de la Cocoa. Or settle onto our porch for a view of the garden with a Sweet Tea Float and slice of Junior’s Cheesecake, delivered weekly from Brooklyn. And don’t forget, our charming venue is perfect for your next occasion - and an even better place to fall in love. BITES, BUBBLES & JAZZ Chez L’Amour provides the perfect setting for a romantic date night, fun outing or special occasion. Social tapas dining, the stellar drink menu and incredible music make Chez L’Amour the perfect place to unwind, celebrate and enjoy friends and family in a cozy atmosphere. ​ Located at 45 San Marco in uptown St. Augustine, Chez L’Amour has its own parking lot providing guests easy access to all that lies within the House of Love. CREATIVE TAPAS Chef Ellie and her team create internationally-inspired dishes using locally-sourced ingredients to deliver fresh, unique flavors. Small plates served in a social dining atmosphere allow culinary explorers to sample an array of flavors with friends and family. Flavor-infused signature cocktails and an extensive list of wine and bubbly cover all needs for aperitifs, pairings and digestifs during happy hour, dinner and after-dinner drinks. SIGNATURE DRINKS St. Augustine’s finest bakery, Creme de la Cocoa, makes Chez L’Amour’s delectable and artisanal desserts, such as the Spanish Magnolia Wedding Cake and Datil Chocolate Cheesecake. LUXURIOUS DESSERTS SPECIAL EVENTS Chez L’Amour is the perfect venue for private events, office parties, rehearsal dinners, birthday celebrations, receptions and banquets. To book your next event, please email: info@bitesbubblesandjazz.com . Chez L’Amour showcases internationally recognized performers, as well as the most talented local and regional musicians. Visit our events page to see the full line-up.
